Audience: Citizen Integrator
Scope: Walk the user through an API integration process leveraging OpenShift, Ansible, Fuse Online, 3scale AMP  

Overview - Deployment process using Ansible - 30 Min

This introduction lab will review the workshop deployment process using Ansible. The lab will follow the deployment process and the agile integration product suite that will be used during the workshop. 

